org.eclipse.ecf.presence
Interface IRosterEntry

All Known Implementing Classes:
RosterEntry
public interface IRosterEntry

Roster entry object. Instances implementing this interface provide information about roster entrys. Implementers of this interface are provided via the IPresenceListener methods. callback

See Also:
IPresenceListener
